<div class="table-responsive">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
      
        <div class="title-web" style="margin-right:10px;">  
            <h3>문의/건의하기</h3>
            <p>업데이트 되었으면 하는 제품, 개선되었으면 하는 점 등 자유롭게 의견을 남겨주세요. </p>
        </div>
        
        <hr style="border: 2px solid #38393b">
        <br>
        
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12" style="padding:0px;">
        <form action="/home/request_reply_ok" method="post">
            <input type="hidden" name="reply_id" value="<%= @one_request.id %>"/>
            <input type="hidden" name="reply_group" value="<%= @group %>"/>
        	<input type="hidden" name="reply_level" value="<%= @level %>"/>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputTitle">제목</label>
                <input type="text" name="title" class="form-control" id="exampleInputTitle" value="&nbsp;&nbsp;[RE]&nbsp;:&nbsp;<%= @one_request.title %>">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="exampleInputContent">내용</label>
                <textarea name="content" class="form-control" rows="5">
                    &#13;
                    &#13;
                    ==============================&#13;
                    <%= @one_request.content %>
                </textarea>
            </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">등록</button>
          <a href="/home/request_view/<%= @one_request.id %>" id="btnCancelRequest" class="btn btn-default">취소</a>
        </form>
        </div>
        
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


